	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />FCEUX tells me that there are <strong>19</strong> 8KB CHR-ROM pages, which is really odd! Memory on the NES should always be in powers of 2, so you should try increasing that to 32 x 8KB, even if you don't have any actual graphics in these 13 pages.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


